c: 17
v: 93
t: "“Kapena nkole nyumba ja golodi, kapena nkwele kwinani, ni nganituŵa tukukulupilile kukwela kwenuko mpaka n’di ntutuluchiisye chitabu chakuti tuchisoomeje.” Jilani (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ): “Kuswejela ni Kwao Ambuje ŵangu! Ana une ndili chilichose, pangaŵaga mundu (jwandumisyidwe kuŵa) ntenga?”"